{"tid":2263344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"法國單日連3案！男闖尼斯教堂揮刀喊「真主至大」 1女遭斬首共3人亡","createTime":"2020-10-29T23:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T03:58:56.000Z","uid":204533,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd1964d2e45ed8a0cbd71972ca9e05369311ea2","tid":2263344,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:01:46.000Z","msg":"法國近期不太平靜，今天一連3起案件。法國東南部城市尼斯（Nice）今天（29日）驚傳持刀攻擊案，事發在教堂，目前已經3人死亡、數人受傷。警方消息指，1名女子慘遭斬首。行兇男子在教堂內被捕，尼斯市長直指此案是恐怖攻擊，歹徒落網時口中一直喊「真主至大」（Allahu Akbar）。在亞維儂也有1名男子叫喊「真主至大」，並持手槍威脅路人，隨後遭警方擊斃。而法國駐沙烏地阿拉伯吉達領事館發生刀襲事件，1名警衛受傷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201029/7K34CBNVQ5BT3P2HTOFXBK24YU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201029%2F7K34CBNVQ5BT3P2HTOFXBK24YU%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=55690b57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201029%2F7K34CBNVQ5BT3P2HTOFXBK24YU%2F&h=7de51261\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201029/7K34CBNVQ5BT3P2HTOFXBK24YU/</a>"},{"pid":"476cd8817bc99d2344a13f3de0782490ad2e2437","tid":2263344,"uid":79793,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:29:30.000Z","msg":"欺善怕惡 唔敢入中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a858a0e7800188fb708558e6b669f310dad087f","tid":2263344,"uid":98692,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都話唔好挑釁伊斯蘭"},{"pid":"e2c2aa284cca8c10121fc0d717b6bb8374822c7e","tid":2263344,"uid":40272,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"476cd8817bc99d2344a13f3de0782490ad2e2437","tid":2263344,"uid":79793,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T23:29:30.000Z","msg":"欺善怕惡 唔敢入中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime